creator: Hubpay
descriptionHtml:
Hubpay is licensed as Money Services Provider by the Abu Dhabi Global Market, to conduct remittances in the UAE.

Hubpay is a digital wallet that lets you make money transfers and payments from the UAE to your family and friends in Asia, and chat to them at the same time.

Hubpay is the lowest cost wallet for remittances and international bill payment, you can send money to banks and agents in a number of countries.

Download the app, complete onboarding digitally and fund your wallet direct from your bank account, all from within the Hubpay wallet!
descriptionShort: Wallet for remittances & bill payment: send money fast, secure at a lowest cost

- We have launched a new corridor.
- We have optimised the overall app experience along with few minor bug fixes.

We have also upgraded the app to allow faster performance at the time of loading money into your Hubpay Wallet Account. Send money home faster than before at NO ADDITIONAL COST. Update the App now!

Hubpay is a digital wallet that enables you to make money transfers and payments from the UAE to your family and friends around the globe. Hubpay allows you to send money to banks and agents in a number of countries around the world.

Download the app, carry out the digital onboarding, and fund your wallet with money straight from your bank account, all from the Hubpay app.
descriptionShort: Low cost, international money transfer app

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Minor enhancements to improve the experience using our app
